- cs.LG (Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of feature selection methods to improve accuracy and reduce the number of features in machine learning models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with techniques for improving the performance of AI systems for natural language processing. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of feature selection methods, which are a common technique in machine learning and data analysis. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly mention the use of neural networks or evolutionary algorithms, but these techniques may be used in the implementation of the morphosyntactic analyzers.
